&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:brain: You will...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn to create viral short-form video, text, and image content on a fast-paced team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to social and other marketing projects with guidance tailored to your personal growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn about social media marketing standards and strategies, and develop exciting and engaging content as a result&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with key partners across marketing, design, product, engineering, and content studio partners to develop ideas and content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor Duolingo’s content and presence on existing channels, such as Twitter, Instagram, and explore new channels and trending content that we should be tapping into&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the coordination of other projects across marketing as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:check:&amp;nbsp;What we’re looking for…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A bachelor&#39;s degree by spring 2027&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-tune with social trends, even before they hit, the ability to respond ASAP to trends/memes to capitalize on those opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid interpersonal skills and enthusiasm for engaging with our social media communities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to relocate to and work in Pittsburgh, PA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:star: Exceptional candidates will have...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A GPA of 3.5+&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Duolingo streak&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A social media internship at another major brand or organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Video/photo editing skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:alert: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you can expect...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A fast-paced social team always on the pulse of culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creative freedom to make what you want&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A powerhouse marketing team to learn from&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:heart: Why you’ll love working here…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Language learning opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Catered in-house lunches and breakfast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company-wide Hackathon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PTO and company holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Frequent company-wide dinners, monthly celebrations, social clubs, and so much more!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;We invest in and support our Duos!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Hourly Range for this internship is:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$38&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$40 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot;&gt;Take a peek at how we care for our employees&#39; holistic well-being with our benefits&lt;a class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot; href=&quot;https://careers.duolingo.com/#benefits&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
